title: Full Show (Ravens vs Bucs TNF preview, Westbrook update, Lakers at Denver preview, Cowboys trade for new DT)
description:
00:00 Ravens at Bucs TNF preview
23:41 Westbrook doubtful to play tonight against Denver with hamstring soreness
52:51 Charles Barkley says age is catching up to Draymond and Klay after 134-105 loss
1:05:13 Cowboys acquire Raiders DT Johnathan Hankins for 2023 6th-round pick
1:17:37 LeBron tweets "Jordan Poole so COLD!!!" during last night's game
1:28:29 Are the New Orleans Pelicans legitimate contenders in the Western Conference?
1:38:20 Scouts reportedly think Matt Ryan's arm is "shot" at age 37
1:47:29 Are the Cowboys not being aggressive enough with Dak back in the lineup?
1:53:39 LeBron and Lakers seek first win of the season in Denver tonight
